descriptions.text: Chennai, once known as Madras, has been welcoming travelers for over 2000 years. Located close to the original port which Roman traders called 'Meliapor' is WelcomHotel Chennai. The hotel provides you the convenience & comfort of home, with warm & efficient service. WelcomHotel Chennai is very conveniently located and central to just about everything - just 15 kilometers from the international airport, 5 kilometers from the railway station, and a short 15-minutes' drive to T. Nagar and Anna Salai - the most popular shopping and commercial areas. WelcomHotel Chennai embodies the harmony of past, present and future, beautifully blending the captivating charm of old world hospitality with efficiency of modern technology. The hotel provides you the convenience & comfort of home, with warm & efficient service. A business hotel built to capture the essence of Chennai's rich history, WelcomHotel Chennai has most prominent architectural features backed with richness of Indian hospitality. Among the most renowned Chennai's 5 star business hotels, WelcomHotel Chennai features warm and efficient service with the latest technology to create a hotel which has redefined comfort. A world of comfort and convenience, with warm & efficient service. WelcomHotel Chennai's reputation as Chennai's leading 5 star business hotels is anchored in many factors. The hotel offers visitors convenience and comfort of home in its 90 spacious guest rooms and suites. With choice of local and international cuisine, quiet spaces for meetings and family occasions, and beautiful banquet areas for conferences and celebrations, the hotel provides all the services a busy traveller might need. Stay with us and experience our warmth and great service.

Fortune Select Palms is located in the heart of Chennai, on the Old Mahabalipuram Road. It is conveniently situated 18 kms from the central railway station of Chennai, 20 kms from the local bus station and 17 km from Chennai Airport. It is a luxurious home to the aesthetic cultural heritage, recreated with state-of art architecture inculcating contemporary modishness. All rooms are well appointed, decorated in a contemporary style. The hotel has an outdoor swimming pool and a gym. There is also a poolside snack bar. For an additional fee, guests may use the health centre, which includes a sauna and steam room, as well as massage and spa facilities. The hotel offers splendid restaurants which serve Indian and exotic cuisines. There is a 24-hour coffee shop, and the Oriental Pavilion restaurant specialises in Chinese cuisine. Come stay with us and experience the real Chennai ambiance.
